result.adr_address: 481 Hennessy Rd, Bowrington, Hong Kong
result.name: MAGMAR

reviews.text: Fabulous, friendly late night bar. Cool atmosphere, laid back music and darts! We were a group mainly of young doctors attending a big international conference. This was the best bar to chill and enjoy our HK vibe. Great bar. 👍🏻
Very poor with cocktail knowledge..... staff friendly but rather poor.... go for an experience leave after one drink
The food was great, the prices for happy hurs is good deal

Great Chill place for drinks 

Also have 1 beer pong table, cards, dice. And  2 kareoke rooms in the back.
非常好的酒吧！有波睇！有鏢掟I
